query:
SELECT 
  a.id as api_id,
  a.name as api_name,
  p.ourPrice,
  p.quantityAvailable,
  a.priority
FROM prices p
INNER JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
INNER JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
WHERE s.id = 60002 
  AND p.countryId = 1
  AND a.active = 1
ORDER BY a.id ASC;
